caption.text:
Tips and tricks on how to do street photography?
.
One thing that I do have in mind, you need to know in what condition you're in right now and what type of composition theory that you're gonna use.
.
Based on my photo here, it was full of people, but not too many. Activities occur on that place too, like capoeira, skating, and many others. So I can take one point of interest like this guy back-flipping and the rest were just concentrating on their own activity, like nothing happened.
.
After you shoot, imagine things that might go wrong according to others. What if some people actually think that the guy back flipping was actually falling from the sky? You just need to be a little bit more creative with this.
.
Thank you and have a good day. üòä
.
Bandung, July 2017
.

caption.text:
First time ever in history, where I will do short introduction about myself and how I view things according to my perspective.
.
Who am I?
an Indonesian street photographer, 20 years old, currently studying chemical engineering in Bandung, moving back and forth to Jakarta.
.
How long have you been doing such thing?
I've been doing street photography for nearly 2 years and I've been in love with it. Also, it is not as expensive as if I were doing landscape, potraits, etc. Meaning, low budget in this category of photography!
.
Why black and white?
Simply, it is full of fantasy. I love the texture, the emotion, the sense of art, and all the things which I could not describe through text.
.
Look through the pictures I photographed recently in Jakarta and I hope you know me even better.
.
Jakarta, July 2017
.

caption.text:
Indonesia Street Project :
.
Sebuah gagasan yang tercipta dari lika-liku beberapa teman-teman penggiat street photography di berbagai wilayah Indonesia.
.
Bertolak dari sebuah forum dan melanjutkan perjalanan street photography indonesia, terbentuklah Indonesia Street Project dengan ingin mengeksplorasi lebih jauh fotografi ruang publik dan jalanan.
.
@indostreetproject menjadi wadah bagi para penggiat street photography untuk berekspresi dan berkarya.
.
Melalui media sosial, kami ingin mencoba berbagi karya maupun proses pembelajaran kami.
.
Ekspresi karya dari teman-teman penggiat Street Photography yakni berupa foto-foto perjalanan, hasil diskusi, karya cetak seperti buku foto maupun zine, serta informasi-informasi terkait acara yang diadakan baik online maupun offline akan kami coba bagikan untuk teman-teman para penggiat street photography di sini.
.
Untuk teman-teman seperjalanan yang ada di Jabodetabek, Jawa Barat, dan Jawa Timur, kami memiliki forum regional yang sekiranya dapat mempertemukan teman-teman untuk bisa sharing dan meetup baik online maupun tatap muka.
.
